OL,3,CKing's Christmas message to reflect on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FThe King's Christmas message will
OL,7,Freflect on his family's battle with
OL,8,Fcancer this year, ITV News Royal
OL,9,FEditor Chris Ship reports
OL,11,FIn a break with recent tradition, King
OL,12,FCharles has chosen to record this
OL,13,Fyear's Christmas message in a tiny
OL,14,Fhospital chapel, to reflect on the
OL,15,Fchallenging year both he and his
OL,16,Fdaughter-in-law, Kate, have
OL,17,Fexperienced battling cancer.
