OL,3,CKing's Christmas message to reflect on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FThe King asked to move the broadcast
OL,7,Flocation away from a royal residence
OL,8,Fand tasked the production team with
OL,9,Ffinding a place that had a health
OL,10,Fconnection but was still a spiritual
OL,11,Fand community space.
OL,13,FThe venue was the Fitzrovia Chapel,
OL,14,Fonce a place of worship and
OL,15,Fcontemplation for patients and medical
OL,16,Fstaff of the Middlesex hospital which
OL,17,Fsurrounded it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
