OL,6,FThe hospital, which was merged with
OL,7,FUniversity College Hospital London,
OL,8,Fwas demolished but the tiny 18th
OL,9,FCentury chapel was left untouched as
OL,10,Fthe site was redeveloped.
OL,12,FIt's the first time since 2006 that a
OL,13,Fmonarch has chosen to record the
OL,14,Ftraditional speech away from a
OL,15,Fresidence like Buckingham Palace or
OL,16,FWindsor Castle.
