OL,3,CKing's Christmas message to reflect on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,FHis previous speeches were recorded at
OL,7,FSt George's Chapel inside Windsor
OL,8,FCastle and in the Centre Room at
OL,9,FBuckingham Palace overlooking The Mall.
OL,11,FFitzrovia Chapel is just moments away
OL,12,Ffrom London's busy Oxford Street shops
OL,13,Fbut provides a quiet, secluded and
OL,14,Fpeaceful place for all faiths.
OL,16,FIt retains a link to the newly-built
OL,17,FUCLH hospital in nearby Euston.
