OL,3,CKing's Christmas message to reflect on
OL,4,Chis and Kate's cancer
OL,6,F"He was pretty surprised and kind of
OL,7,Fdelighted, as far as I can tell, from
OL,8,Fcoming in and discovering it", said
OL,9,FCarla Whalen, chair of the Fitzrovia
OL,10,FChapel Foundation's board of trustees.
OL,12,FA royal source described the King as
OL,13,Fbeing "bowled over" by its beauty and
OL,14,Fthe fact that its location is largely
OL,15,Funknown.
