OL,6,FMs Whalen added: "He was very
OL,7,Finterested in the marble, there's 40
OL,8,Ftypes of marble here and lots of
OL,9,Fdifferent designs and he wanted to
OL,10,Flearn about the history of the chapel
OL,11,Fand some of the people who are
OL,12,Fcommemorated here.
OL,14,FA palace source said: "Obviously it
OL,15,Fmade sense it had some form of health
OL,16,Fconnection, because that of course has
OL,17,Fbeen a dominant theme for the family
OL,18,Fin all kinds of different ways.
