OL,6,F"Secondly and equally importantly,
OL,7,Fthat it should speak in some way of
OL,8,Fbringing communities
OL,9,Ftogether...thirdly of course it does
OL,10,Fhelps if it looks rather beautiful and
OL,11,Fis a place of spiritual solace and
OL,12,Freflection."
OL,14,FThe Christmas message will be
OL,15,Fbroadcast on most TV channels at 3pm,
OL,16,Flocal time, in the UK and the other
OL,17,FCommonwealth Realms.
